WEBVTT

00:03:59.266 --> 00:04:00.789
Love?

00:04:00.813 --> 00:04:04.640
Watch for this formula in books,
movies, and TV shows you come across.

00:04:04.664 --> 00:04:06.385
You will certainly see it again.

00:04:06.409 --> 00:04:08.732
But also be sensitive
to it in your own life.

00:04:09.616 --> 00:04:11.274
Listen for your call to adventure.

00:04:12.083 --> 00:04:13.641
Accept the challenge.

00:04:13.665 --> 00:04:16.410
Conquer your fear
and claim the treasure you seek.

00:04:17.293 --> 00:04:18.569
And then,

00:04:18.593 --> 00:04:19.983
do it all over again.